<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-40-0943 </DOCNO><TEXT>This bibliography contains citations concerning materials used for thethermal insulation of buildings. Consumer acceptance of materials andweatherproofing options are included. Insulation in new and retrofittedbuildings is discussed. Residential buildings, earth sheltered structures,greenhouses, and animal houses are among the structures studied. Infraredthermal sensing of heat loss, insulation placement, multilayer partitionwalls, and insulating windows are briefly considered. (This updated bibliographycontains 244 citations, 92 of which are new entries to the previous edition.)</TEXT></DOC>